            <scopecontent id="aspace_02615d29b38fade567dd98fd3eadb9ca">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Boxes 3-4 hold Series II, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                     <part>Other Papers</part>
                  </title>, which includes manuscripts, photographs and printed material by other people. Groesbeck's collection of poetry clippings is arranged alphabetically by author, except for her oversize collection which is in its original order.</p>
            </scopecontent>
